  "detailed_description": "<strong>Circus of TimTim</strong> is a Stealth Horror Survival Game about two siblings trying to sneak inside the most hunted carnival of all time to recover lost items with a metal detector device, however enemies are roaming around and they can hear your every step in the circus. <br><br>This is a first person stealth adventure horror game that takes place inside a run-down circus. Play as a sibling tasked to find her brother's missing items after an incident that occurred there, but beware as strange things are happening. Roam around, stealth, hide, run and survive to to uncover the secrets of what happened at the Circus of TimTim - a once fun place turned deadly.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/d631306e166e794936a4b389fcef9cac.poster.avif?t=1711126873\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/d631306e166e794936a4b389fcef9cac.webm?t=1711126873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/d631306e166e794936a4b389fcef9cac.mp4?t=1711126873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Free to explore the run-down circus</strong><br>Explore the circus and the mysteries that lies ahead. You can freely roam around the carnival to finish your tasks, but beware as something will not allow you to stay there. You have to hide and use stealth in order to evade the enemies.<br><br><strong>Equipped with a metal detector, to find items!</strong><br>You will be equipped with a metal detector to find items lost inside the circus, however while the metal detector can aid you and help you find items quickly, the beeping sound that it will make will attract enemies to your location - so choose wisely!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use tools to lead you to your next objective - but careful as enemies can hear the beep!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/21f57959aacb4e2291218dea793edc17.poster.avif?t=1711126873\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/21f57959aacb4e2291218dea793edc17.webm?t=1711126873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/21f57959aacb4e2291218dea793edc17.mp4?t=1711126873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the ruins and death of what was once a fun-family circus!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/d3cd5a2487e38b54a27040bf3d4bf6b8.poster.avif?t=1711126873\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/d3cd5a2487e38b54a27040bf3d4bf6b8.webm?t=1711126873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/d3cd5a2487e38b54a27040bf3d4bf6b8.mp4?t=1711126873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Make sure not to get lost in it's beauty, because it can be deadly.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/79527111b4663700169cfa7736d58c77.poster.avif?t=1711126873\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/79527111b4663700169cfa7736d58c77.webm?t=1711126873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/79527111b4663700169cfa7736d58c77.mp4?t=1711126873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the insides of every corner of the carnival and leave no stone unturned!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/404c2b8f7851042f2aae8614616fbfd6.poster.avif?t=1711126873\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/404c2b8f7851042f2aae8614616fbfd6.webm?t=1711126873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/404c2b8f7851042f2aae8614616fbfd6.mp4?t=1711126873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find items that can help you in the circus.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/ea27ce8295bf767042cc80c2b6099714.poster.avif?t=1711126873\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/ea27ce8295bf767042cc80c2b6099714.webm?t=1711126873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/ea27ce8295bf767042cc80c2b6099714.mp4?t=1711126873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Filled with threats, that you need to evade by distracting them or using stealth!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/6bc7fbd8349907f1aa0bf90058cce08b.poster.avif?t=1711126873\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/6bc7fbd8349907f1aa0bf90058cce08b.webm?t=1711126873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/6bc7fbd8349907f1aa0bf90058cce08b.mp4?t=1711126873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Lurking at every corner of the circus, so always be aware!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/a4104be00a56ce75ca33630d25268435.poster.avif?t=1711126873\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/a4104be00a56ce75ca33630d25268435.webm?t=1711126873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/a4104be00a56ce75ca33630d25268435.mp4?t=1711126873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Making noise, stepping on rubber ducks and more can attract the enemy!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/8cfd99bf11346b40fc745cc5a7bf1eb0.poster.avif?t=1711126873\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/8cfd99bf11346b40fc745cc5a7bf1eb0.webm?t=1711126873\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/8cfd99bf11346b40fc745cc5a7bf1eb0.mp4?t=1711126873\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find tickets and exchange them to open doors by the creepy booth master! </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697070/extras/18ad9ce8e952d3636d742c2b2e7a8977.poster.avif?t=17